**Consistent sizing:**

```tsx
// Define standard sizes
const ICON_SIZES = {
  sm: "w-4 h-4",
  md: "w-5 h-5",
  lg: "w-6 h-6",
  xl: "w-8 h-8",
} as const;

import { Home } from "lucide-react";

export function Icon({ size = "md" }: { size?: keyof typeof ICON_SIZES }) {
  return <Home className={ICON_SIZES[size]} />;
}
```

## Variants or Exceptions

- Custom icons (logos, illustrations) can be imported as SVG from `public/icons/`.
- Existing projects with other icon libraries should progressively migrate to Lucide.

